data.title: Organize your TVPage
data.description: It's easy to Organize videos on your TVPage. Create Channels if you'd like to place your videos in the right category and context. Sort the order of your Videos in each TVPage and Channel. Use the Clipboard to drag Videos or Channels aside while you are thinking about where they should go. Contact support@tvpage.com with any questions.
